                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390916-name-1379" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390916-name-1379" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390916-name-1379" type="surname" value="HOWARD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390916-name-1379" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>RICHARD HOWARD</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Herbert's-buildings, Southwark. The prisoner was in my employ—if he received money from any of my custom<lb></lb>ers it was his duty to pay it to me as soon as he returned—I did not send him to Mr. Ashton on the 26th of August to receive money—Mr. Ashton owed me 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 19<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., if he paid that to the prisoner it was his duty to pay it to me—he did not pay me, and he did not return—he had paid me money he had received from Mr. Ashton before—he worked for me be<lb></lb>tween six and seven years.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
