                  </hi>. On the 26th of August I owed the prosecutor 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 19<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., which I paid to the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
