                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable M</hi> 126.) I took the prisoner, and told him what it was for—he said, "I am sorry it was not 15<hi rend="italic">l</hi>."</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I said no such thing—I went to Mr. Ashton's in the morn<lb></lb>ing, and got the money—I met a young man, and went to Bermondsey to see his father—when I had got a glass of two more I staid away from work—I had no thoughts of spending it—I spent some of the money—I went as far as Woolwich with him, as he was going to sea—I sat down and went to sleep, and lost a sovereign and a half.</p>
